Philharmonia Orchestra of London Sound Samples

Thousands of free, downloadable sound samples specially recorded by Philharmonia Orchestra players. 
These samples are suitable for creating any kind of music, no matter what style.


http://www.philharmonia.co.uk/explore/make_music


License: You are free to use these samples as you wish, including releasing them as part of a commercial work. 
The only restriction is they must not be sold or made available 'as is' (i.e. as samples or as a sampler instrument).

